[normal], a cop
[normal]y
[normal] of which is 
[normal]enclosed
[normal].
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Home Group is a Registered Pro
[normal]vider and as such 
[normal]is 
[normal]subject to regulation by the HCA
[normal].
[normal] 
[normal]I hope you will appreciate that as the 
[normal]guarantee was 
[normal]issue
[normal]d over 
[normal]26
[normal] year
[normal]s
[normal] ago, it is difficult for me to ascertain the rationale for extending the guarantee at the time.
